{"tid":55801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"英國行程一問","createTime":"2016-12-26T16:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T17:29:47.000Z","uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66c9841d772a06171443b04034997aaa883328be","tid":55801,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"一月中去英國7日<br />\n係Heathrow 落機 暫時想去London Brighton Cambridge 同湖區<br />\n好想去埋oxford<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但冇時間去 定係我應該唔去湖區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e628f5c2eb0a236933ba1fe1daa3118883a20cd4","tid":55801,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"Lake District好靚，但如果你只係有時間去lake district啲major town而無時間行山/去荒蕪啲嘅區分，你會發現自己俾蝗包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5df16357552e51c3b91d71be492f57c8f8d17f5","tid":55801,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lake District好靚，但如果你只係有時間去lake district啲major town而無時間行山/去荒蕪啲嘅區分，你會發現自己俾蝗包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打算去2日1夜 中午到 夜晚走 夠唔夠去major town 外既地方？<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cbf54908e202880203331beeda11c301b4b566","tid":55801,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"老實講，唔建議去埋湖區<br />\n一來太唔順路，二來湖區要去埋附近D小鎮慢慢遊覽先好玩，否則如果你時間唔夠，淨係行Windermere既話，恐怕你會失望"},{"pid":"255e531917ab390c135ec76501b9a16069706228","tid":55801,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lake District好靚，但如果你只係有時間去lake district啲major town而無時間行山/去荒蕪啲嘅區分，你會發現自己俾蝗包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打算去2日1夜 中午到 夜晚走 夠唔夠去major town 外既地方？<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去下Ambleside，Windermere搭巴士去半個鐘之內到，不過班次疏而且尾班車好早開"},{"pid":"86c7aa3f15ec5583ac4cbd941f6423bcb2ff24df","tid":55801,"uid":52968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6bb75a4340c0d7c9730f211c783fd82a39eb391c","tid":55801,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lake District好靚，但如果你只係有時間去lake district啲major town而無時間行山/去荒蕪啲嘅區分，你會發現自己俾蝗包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打算去2日1夜 中午到 夜晚走 夠唔夠去major town 外既地方？<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去下Ambleside，Windermere搭巴士去半個鐘之內到，不過班次疏而且尾班車好早開</blockquote><br />\n當我冇講過，諗諗下Ambleside都算係major town"},{"pid":"f998b43ff5a8f6e5c8479010f32f03bb52cb2689","tid":55801,"uid":32947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"London唔好留咁耐 去完啲指定動作好走 留番啲時間去第二度好過 thanks me later<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a696bd801b2099049d4e85fadb50ea865fce8ec9","tid":55801,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"同埋如果你去得Lake District，不妨順路去埋Lancaster, Liverpool, Manchester"},{"pid":"f5b43479160179bbdb69a6fccdf7ee2e4db47e47","tid":55801,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lake District好靚，但如果你只係有時間去lake district啲major town而無時間行山/去荒蕪啲嘅區分，你會發現自己俾蝗包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\